OL,3,CSouthern Water boss says water outage
OL,4,Cbefore Christmas was 'unacceptable'
OL,6,FThe Chief Executive of Southern Water
OL,7,Fhas told MPs that a water outage which
OL,8,Fleft thousands of customers in
OL,9,FHampshire with no supply, just days
OL,10,Fbefore Christmas, was "completely
OL,11,Funacceptable".
OL,13,FLawrence Gosden said the company's
OL,14,Fresponse to the disruption had "not
OL,15,Fbeen good enough".
OL,17,FOn Tuesday 21 January, Lawrence
OL,18,FGosden, said: "It is a completely
OL,19,Funacceptable position for there to
OL,20,Fhave been any incidents.
