OL,3,CSouthern Water boss says water outage
OL,4,Cbefore Christmas was 'unacceptable'
OL,6,FAffected Southern Water customer and
OL,7,FSouthampton resident, Peter Eades, is
OL,8,Fangry after being offered just #100 in
OL,9,Fcompensation.
OL,11,FPeter Eades said: "I wouldn't allow
OL,12,Fthese two (Southern Water bosses) to
OL,13,Fchange a washer on a tap.
OL,15,F"They don't deserve the bonuses
OL,16,Fthey're boasting about. We've suffered
OL,17,Fall the way through this. But it's not
OL,18,Fjust me, it's the 60-odd-thousand
OL,19,Fpeople who were involved."
