OL,6,FSewage spills were also raised by MPs
OL,7,Fand the Chief Executive was asked for
OL,8,Fhis message to the seaside communities.
OL,10,FHe said: "It genuinely breaks my
OL,11,Fheart. I am from the region, I grew up
OL,12,Fin the region and I live in the region.
OL,14,F"The position that we are in, is one
OL,15,Fwhich is genuinely, genuinely
OL,16,Fterrible. The context is that bathing
OL,17,Fwaters have improved drastically."
